 Aisha Buhari The First Lady of the Republic of Nigeria, Aisha Buhari is has returned to Nigeria after spending a little over six months in United Arab Emirates. According to report the first lady took care of other personal important issues after attending the wedding of her daughter Hanan. Mrs. Buhari arrived in Nigeria on Wednesday night, March 17, 2021 and is going about her normal duties in the statehouse Abuja. The first lady recently celebrated her 50th birthday Whiles she was in Dubai ,United Arab Emirates.